START

DISPLAY welcome message

DISPLAY list of available languages
INPUT choiceOfLanguage

SWITCH (choiceOfLanguage)
    CASE valid:
        DISPLAY confirmation message
    DEFAULT:
        DISPLAY invalid choice message

DISPLAY list of medical fields
INPUT choiceOfField

SWITCH (choiceOfField)
    CASE valid:
        DISPLAY confirmation message
    DEFAULT:
        DISPLAY invalid choice message

SET numberOfLanguages = 6
SET numberOfCountries = 11
SET possibility = numberOfLanguages * numberOfCountries

CALCULATE probability = 1 / possibility

INITIALIZE random seed using current time
GENERATE randomCountry between 0 and 10

DISPLAY assigned country using:
    countries[choiceOfLanguage - 1][randomCountry]

DISPLAY explanation of probability calculation

END
